body:
After reading the Updated Biography from the Noxian Lore update, I&#039;m actually Impressed with how the Lore is being rewritten since it explains alot about champions &amp; gives us insight as to what kind of person/creature they are in the world of Runeterra.
What stuck out for me &amp; pretty much has my full attention is Leblanc&#039;s relationship to Mordekaiser. Previously, I thought Mordekaiser had ties to the Shadow Isles &amp; nothing more than that. Now I feel like there&#039;s more to Mordekaiser than we&#039;re being led onto since they mentioned the Immortal Bastion (which basically was his Stronghold) in the New Lore.
Honestly between the Lore Updates &amp; some Interactions I&#039;m seeing with Mordekaiser, I&#039;m hoping Mordekaiser is selected sometime later this year for a VGU. This way we can see how he is connected to the Immortal Bastion &amp; Noxus in the new continuity. 

&quot;My army will soon storm your gates, Revenant.&quot; - {{champion:83}} 
&quot;You give the dead purpose, Mordekaiser. I give them meaning.&quot; - {{champion:30}}
